Display Stack Layer Junction data on the PAAM deconflict screen so users can quickly review each application’s PAAM-related details in one place.

Show the following fields in the PAAM records table:

Application Name
Operational Status
PAAM Manual

Acceptance Criteria

The PAAM deconflict screen displays records from Stack_Layer_Junction__c.

The table shows:

Application Name from Name__c
Operational Status from TPM_App_Stack__r.App__r.Operational_Status__c
PAAM Manual from Stack_Layer_Config__r.Name

Users can search by application name, operational status, or PAAM manual.

The screen supports ownership filters like My Primary Apps, My All Apps, and All Apps.

Data should load correctly without impacting existing PAAM screen functionality.
